quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  21,51,Mazima twawa Ibrahim obulungamubwe okuva oluberyeberye era twali tumanyi ebimukwatako
  21,52,"Jjukira bwe yagamba kitaawe n'abantu be nti: bifaananyi ki bino, ebyo mmwe bye mulemeddeko"
  21,53,Nebagamba nti twasanga bakadde baffe nga byebasinza
  21,54,(Ibrahim) naagamba nti mazima mmwe ne bakadde ba mmwe mwali mu bubuze obw'olwatu
  21,55,Nebagamba nti otuleetedde mazima oba oli mu ba kazannyirizi
  21,56,"Naagamba nti wabula Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe, ye Mukama omulabirizi w'eggulu (omusanvu) n'ensi oyo eyabitonda nange ku ekyo ndi omu ku bajulizi"
  21,57,Era ndayira Katonda amasanamu ga mmwe nja kugasalira amagezi singa munaaba mugaleseewo ne mubaako wemulaga
  21,58,"(Yagabetenta) naagafuula bubajjo okugyako (essanamu) erigasinga obunene, olwo nno badde gye liri (lye baba babuuza)"
  21,59,"(Bwe badda) nebagamba nti ani akoze kino ku ba katonda baffe, mazima yye ali mu beeyisa obubi"
  21,60,Nebagamba nti twawulidde omuvubuka ayitibwa Ibrahim nga agoogerako
  21,61,Nebagamba nti kale mumuleete mu maaso g'abantu bamuweeko obujulizi
  21,62,"(Bwe baamutuusa) nebamugamba nti: Gwe wakoze kino ku ba katonda baffe owange Ibrahim"
  21,63,"Naabagamba nti: nedda omukulu waabwe ono ye yakikoze, kale mubabuuze bwe baba nga baatula"
  21,64,"Nebeetunulako nebagamba nti mazima mmwe, mmwe abeeyisa obubi"
  21,65,"Ate oluvanyuma (lw'ekyo) beekyusa, (mu kifo ky'okwenenya baalemera ku bukaafiiri era nebagamba nti) mazima okimanyi nti amasanamu ago tegoogera"
  21,66,(Ibrahim) naagamba nti ate muva ku Katonda nemusinza ebitabagasa kantu konna wadde okubatuusaako akabi
  21,67,"Kivve ku mmwe, lwaki musinza ebintu ebirala nemuleka Katonda abaffe temutegeera"
  21,68,Nebagamba nti (oba bwatyo bwagamba) mumwokye mutaase ba katonda ba mmwe bwe muba nga mulina kye munaakola
  21,69,Netugamba nti owange muliro beera bunnyogovu era mirembe ku Ibrahim
  21,70,Baayagala okumukolera olukwe naye twabafuula abataalufunamu
  21,71,Netumuwonya netuwonya ne Luutu netubatwala mu nsi gye twawa omukisa ku lw'ebitonde
  21,72,"Twamugabira Ishaka ne Yakubu nga nnyongeza, bonna twabafuula balongoofu"
  21,73,"Era twabafuula abakulembeze nga balungamya olw'ekiragiro kyaffe, era twabatumira nti (bateekwa) okukola obulungi n'okuyimirizaawo e sswala n'okutoola zzaka era baali batusinza"
  21,74,Ne Luutu twamuwa okusengejja ensonga n'okumanya era twamuwonya netumuggya mu kitundu ekyali kikola ebyonoono mazima bo baali bantu ba kibi aboonoonyi
  21,75,Era twamuyingiza mu kusaasira kwaffe mazima yye wa mu balongoofu
  21,76,Era (mujjukire) Nuhu bwe yasaba oluberyeberye nga abantu (bamulemeredde) netwanukula okusaba kwe netumuwonya wamu n’abantube mu kabi akanene
  21,77,"Netumutaasa ku bantu abo abaalimbisa ebigambo byaffe, mazima bbo baali bantu ba kibi netubazikiriza bonna"
  21,78,"Era mujjukire Dauda ne Sulaiman mu kiseera bombi bwe baalamula omusango ogukwata ku nnimiro, embuzi z’abantu bwe zaaliiramu, era ku kulamula kwabwe twali bajulizi"
  21,79,"(Omusango ogwo) twawa Sulaiman okutegeera obulungi, naye buli omu twamuwa okugoba ensonga n’okumanya, era twagondeza Dauda ensozi nga zitendereza, n’ebinyonyi bwe bityo, (buli lwe yatenderezanga nga nabyo bitendereza). Era ebyo twali tusobolera ddala okubikola"
  21,80,"Era twamuyigiriza okukola ebyambalo bya mmwe (eby'entalo) biryoke bibakuume ku buzibu bwa mmwe, abaffe mmwe mwebaza"
  21,81,Era Sulaiman twamugondeza empewo ekungunta nga etambulira ku kiragirokye neEgenda eri ensi eyo gye twawa omukisa. Era twali tumanyi buli kintu
  21,82,Ne mu zi Sitane mwalimu ezibbira mu nnyanja ku lulwe nga zikola n'emirimu emirala egitali ogwo era ffe twazikuumanga